   <description>
    <narrative xml:lang="EN">This grant provides financial support to IFRC&apos;s Surge Desk for the IFRC ERU review taking place in Q4 2020 - Q2 2021. Please note that the initial proposed timeframe for completing the review was Q1 2021. However, the GAD was revised after the project lead, head of ESTA, agreed to extend the timeframe after a request from IFRC.&#xC2;&#xA0;
As highlighted in the GAD, the final narrative report that will be submitted to BRC will be the review report. IFRC is therefore not required to provide a standard narrative report.&#xC2;&#xA0;
BRC will also be part of the ERU review team, with one of our technical staff providing support/input, and we will therefore follow the review process closely.&#xC2;&#xA0;
For further information/questions please contact grant admin Anna O Eriksson</narrative>
   </description>
